00:02:16.370 --> 00:02:20.290
So as you see me demonstrate here, all I'm
doing is really changing the pressure that

00:02:20.290 --> 00:02:23.819
I'm applying through my forefingers and through
my thumb.

00:02:23.819 --> 00:02:29.360
As I roll out, I want to take all four fingers
off and literally push the Dumbbell away from

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:31.360
me with my just my thumb.

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:35.660
That allows the Dumbbell to spin inside of
my hand and not get slowed down or dragged

00:02:35.660 --> 00:02:36.879
down by friction.

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:41.270
But as I come back, what I want to do is then,
grasp with the four fingers and then release

00:02:41.270 --> 00:02:42.291
