00:02:42.291 --> 00:02:45.670
So that now, I'm able to actually roll the
Dumbbell back.

00:02:45.670 --> 00:02:49.240
If you grip too hard in both directions, you're
going to wind up not allowing the Dumbbell

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:51.599
